            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p>在本模块结束时，您将能够：</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "list",
          "variant": "bulleted",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "list_style": "bulleted",
          "items_html": [
            "<p>定义机械罐子结构和垂直液体冷却歧管集成。</p>",
            "<p>演示节点插入期间Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling参与的三个阶段。 &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>比较跨超大规模和企业合作伙伴的 Helios 架构的实际实现。</p>",
            "<p>预测即将到来的数据中心宏观趋势，包括极高电压限制和光互连规模。</p>"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "continue",
          "variant": "continue",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
