        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "text_aside",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "image_size": "medium",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "image_role": "content",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/orw-liquid-cooling-mechanics.jpg",
            "alt": "ORW Liquid cooling mechanics.jpg",
            "source_asset": "ORW Liquid cooling mechanics.jpg",
            "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
            "bytes": 264157,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 950
            }
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">将重型 IT 设备连接到装满的机架内的高压液体歧管需要自动化精度，以消除人为错误和灾难性泄漏风险。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">单击下图探索 Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling (PBMC) 的三个不同机械阶段接合。</span></p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "divider",
          "variant": "divider",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "labeled_graphic",
          "variant": "labeledgraphic",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1",
            "media_width_variant": "medium"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "枢轴",
              "x": "14.9045163109189",
              "y": "51.73941798941799",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>在流体密封相遇之前，联轴器接合出色的机械枢轴机构。该浮动枢轴自动使连接组件自动居中，以物理方式吸收由连接到节点底盘后部的刚性、重型液体软管引起的任何角度偏差或结构阻力。</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "管理错位",
              "x": "50.04712785993304",
              "y": "56.962083281663354",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>当重型服务器节点在结构罐式外壳内向前滑动时，插头和插座流体连接器在机架框架深处相互接近。 <br><br>在此初始阶段，硬件必须动态补偿标准制造公差、物理框架弯曲以及服务器机箱的巨大重力。</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "流体锁",
              "x": "89.04638381231399",
              "y": "51.42857142857142",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>在插入的最后阶段，连接器干净地滑动在一起并发出明确的机械咔嗒声，建立完全密封的流体路径，能够处理用于冷却人工智能加速器的高流量。 <br><br>完全配合后，浮动机构将机械调节公差与主密封区域分离，确保零泄漏锁定，无需任何手动干预。</p>"
            }
          ],
          "media": {
