            "bytes": 231822,
            "dimensions": {
              "width": 911,
              "height": 717,
              "originalWidth": 1280,
              "originalHeight": 720
            }
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">人工智能计算的快速发展继续以指数速度加速。 </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">为了确保您的设施基础设施保持高度可扩展性，工程师必须设计能够承受下一波宏观技术转变的框架。</span></p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">单击&nbsp;每张卡，探索即将到来的基础设施趋势，将Open Rack Wide架构推向其设计极限。</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>LVDC 内向直流电和更高电压的过渡</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">随着功率密度需求飙升至每个外壳数百千瓦，传统的低压传输路径遇到了严重的物理和效率障碍。社区正在积极探索向更高工作电压阈值的大规模架构转变，这将大大减少原铜电缆体积需求并减轻母线网格上严重的电线压降。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>光纤和无线互连 </p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">下一代扩展网络需要极高的数据吞吐量速度和几乎零延迟的延迟瓶颈。未来的 ORW 迭代将无缝结合直接光学互连方案和无电缆背板配置，在相邻服务器容器之间平稳移动大量高密度数据流，而不会阻塞结构性热排气通道。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>后勤之战：托管与专用数据中心</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">部署超重型、高密度、液冷集群在行业中造成了严重的物流差异。标准商业托管设施必须积极升级其强化地板限制、高架码头基础设施和集中式流体设施，以匹配一级超大规模企业构建的定制、专用混凝土和冷却环境。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
