    {
      "id": 6,
      "slug": "knowledge-check",
      "title": "知识检查",
      "description_html": "",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.94118\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: inherit\" data-color-scope=\"outer\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span>测试本模块的知识。为每个问题选择最佳答案，然后提交。</span></span></span></span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "full",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "card_mode": "WHITE",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 0,
            "padding_bottom": 0,
            "custom_padding_top": 0,
            "custom_padding_bottom": 0,
            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/black-banner-intro.png",
            "alt": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "source_asset": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 12283,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 295
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling（PBMC）内部的机械枢轴机构在节点插入过程中解决什么具体问题？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它将交流电转换为直流电路径。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它自动补偿角度不对中和重型软管影响，以防止连接器损坏。 </p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>当液体流速波动时，它会限制内部服务器风扇。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它锁定前端装载服务器手柄以防止意外提取。</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！ PBMC 利用精确的机械枢轴来吸收结构公差变量和重型软管阻力，确保每次都能实现安全、自对准的连接。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正确。枢轴组件的主要功能是纯粹的机械对准。它动态吸收角度公差和重型软管影响，以引导流体连接器实现完美密封。</p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>哪种实现可作为高度优化的参考解决方案，旨在大规模验证基本的 1200 毫米 ORW 框架标准？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>Open Rack V1 历史模板</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>传统19英寸EIA服务器机架</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>AMD Helios 参考架构</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>标准风冷 HPR 配置 </p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！ Helios 作为旗舰参考实例，展示了巨大的硅足迹和复杂的流体歧管如何在扩展的宽框架格式中完美集成。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正确。 Helios 参考架构是为证明开放式 1200 毫米 ORW 规范的水平体积和组件集成而开发的主要平台。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>基础设施运营商应该去哪里找到 Open Rack Wide 框架的开源 CAD 模型、完整的工程源文件和最终的社区技术规范？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>本地硬件供应商私有目录</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>标准商业搜索引擎图像存储库</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>通用专有数据中心设施手册</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>OCP 贡献数据库</p>",
              "correct": true
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！ OCP 贡献数据库托管对所有基本规范、工程文件和结构模型的完整、供应商中立的访问，供全球社区使用。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正确。所有官方社区规范、接受的设计和生产就绪的 CAD 源文件都直接托管在公共、供应商中立的 OCP 贡献数据库中。</p>"
        },
        {
